fr.polytech.prd.plateforme.model

Class TVChannel

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.polytech.prd.plateforme.model.TVChannel

  • public class TVChannel
extends java.lang.Object
    TVChannel class represents an object TV Channel It has two arguments:
    • the channel Name
    • the channel address to read the stream from. Example, for TF1, the address is https://www.tf1.fr/tf1/direct
    Author:
    Romain Rousseau
